{"tid":1562092,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"各區連儂牆要人！！！！！","createTime":"2019-09-12T01:15:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-12T02:36:41.000Z","uid":182596,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"923886a52ecc74a3bf55982c18b36e0afa013291","tid":1562092,"uid":182596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T01:15:09.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">連儂牆撕一貼百唔係得個講字</span><br />\n好多街坊老人家仲有八卦嘅小朋友都會經過停低睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n近日各區連儂牆接二連三受破壞<br />\n唔緊要 反正舊嘅文宣都要換<br />\n亦都證明左連儂牆有一定嘅威力<br />\n但係好明顯貼文宣嘅手足少左好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望有少少經濟能力嘅手足可以print啲文宣圖<br />\n無嘅經過貼幾張memo都好 <br />\n各位巴絲打可唔可以陪小妹一齊做文宣啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n日日自己貼好孤單好攰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n(個人覺得街坊動源力強 連儂牆功不可沒) <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n4h7WTn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn4h7WTn.jpg&h=4b209263&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d17799f29302ee1a59c4d9797785583c7a9af492","tid":1562092,"uid":76702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T01:15:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bd7a81d266fbfcbdbf9e425a8fbedf7ef21bef83","tid":1562092,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T01:15:54.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src